snippet.title: Celebrities Furiously React to Hollywood Protecting Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Celebrities Furiously React to Hollywood Protecting Amber Heard!
The case against Johnny Depp has been going on for so long as Depp tries to recover his reputation in the midst of all the accusations laid against him by his ex-wife, Amber Heard.
Despite the numerous pieces of evidence that point at Amber being the actual bad guy, she still has managed to get the court and even Hollywood on her side.

Here on Film Streak we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assure that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning you favorite actors!
